\n━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━\n\n1. SETUP: Enter your LiteLLM proxy URL and API key in the Proxy Config node.\n   Your proxy must have a Veo 3 model configured (e.g. via Google AI Studio or Vertex AI).\n\n2. TEXT-TO-VIDEO: Just type a prompt and hit Queue. That's it!\n\n3. IMAGE-TO-VIDEO: Connect a LoadImage node to the \"first_frame\" input.\n   This will use your image as the starting frame. Duration auto-sets to 8s.\n\n4. INTERPOLATION: Connect images to BOTH \"first_frame\" and \"last_frame\".\n   Veo will generate a video that transitions between the two frames.\n\nMODELS:\n  - veo-3.1-generate-preview      (highest quality, 4K, with audio)\n  - veo-3.1-fast-generate-preview  (faster, lower cost)\n\nNOTES:\n  - Supports 720p, 1080p, and 4K resolution\n  - 1080p/4K and reference images require 8s duration (auto-enforced)\n  - Generation takes 1-6 minutes. Adjust max_wait_time if needed.\n  - Output frames go to VHS Video Combine for MP4 export."],"color":"#353","bgcolor":"#464"},{"id":1,"type":"JunoProxyConfig","pos":[24,180],"size":[350,120],"flags":{},"order":0,"mode":0,"inputs":[{"localized_name":"proxy_url","name":"proxy_url","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"proxy_url"},"link":null},{"localized_name":"api_key","name":"api_key","type":"STRING","widget":{"name":"api_key"},"link":null}],"outputs":[{"localized_name":"proxy_config","name":"proxy_config","type":"JUNO_PROXY_CONFIG","slot_index":0,"links":[1]}],"properties":{"aux_id":"clg236/juno-comfyui-nodes","ver":"b31ab01e55a41cd59fb9fc2cb00f9e327fefc89e","Node name for S&R":"JunoProxyConfig"},"widgets_values":["http://localhost:4000",""],"color":"#322","bgcolor":"#533"}],"links":[[1,1,0,2,0,"JUNO_PROXY_CONFIG"],[3,2,0,4,0,"IMAGE"]],"groups":[{"id":1,"title":"1. Proxy Config","bounding":[-12,72,420,336],"color":"#8c3b3b","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":2,"title":"2. Veo 3 Video Generation","bounding":[420,72,504,648],"color":"#3f789e","font_size":24,"flags":{}},{"id":3,"title":"3. Preview","bounding":[984,72,440,